# Using in a build

To use ${solution_name} in a build, add it as a Build Step after the Build Step that builds your project, and complete the following:

1. *Polaris Cli Installation*: Select the name of the ${polaris_cli_name} installation.
1. *Polaris Arguments*: The arguments you want passed to the ${polaris_cli_name} (for example: *analyze*).
1. *Wait for Issues*: DO NOT CHECK THIS BOX OR DISASTER WILL ENSUE!!
1. Click Save.